<item>
            <title>[SOLR-5357] Schemaless example does not contain a solr.xml</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-5357</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The example-schemaless example does not contain solr.xml&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So when you run the example using &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt; java -Dsolr.solr.home=example-schemaless/solr -jar start.jar &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt; Solr fails to start and an exception is thrown.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;Caused by: org.apache.solr.common.SolrException: solr.xml does not exist in /Users/varun/search-work/lucene-trunk/solr/example/example-schemaless/solr/solr.xml cannot start Solr
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
